# Build context is the repo root for all Dockerfiles. Keep it lean: exclude VCS,
# installed deps (the image runs `pnpm install` fresh), build outputs (regenerated
# by `pnpm -r build`), the Go binary, docs, and local scratch. Do NOT exclude
# package manifests, lockfiles, packages/ sources, tsconfig*, .npmrc, or docker/.
.git
.gitignore
**/node_modules
**/dist
*.tsbuildinfo
/worktreedb-build
.superpowers
.devdb-data
.idea
.DS_Store
.claude
docs
